About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2", the sixth film in the YRF Spy Universe, starring Hrithik Roshan, NTR and Kiara Advani, directed by Ayan Mukerji, released on 14 August 2025. "Alpha", the seventh film in the franchise and Hindi cinema’s first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, will release on 25 December 2025.

snippet.title: Dolphins Up Close with Bertie Gregory | Official Trailer | National Geographic
snippet.description:
Bertie Gregory heads to the Azores, a remote island chain in the Atlantic Ocean. Surrounded by Europe’s largest marine protected area, these waters are a vital stop for migrating predators, drawn here by rich feeding grounds. It’s the perfect time for Bertie to capture a rare natural spectacle—when elusive predators unite to hunt dense shoals of fish called bait balls. But with unpredictable storms, filming won’t be easy. During his journey, Bertie also explores the region’s dark history of marine exploitation. By meeting an ex-whaler turned whale spotter, he discovers how the end of whaling transformed the Azores into a sanctuary, allowing marine life to return and delicate food chains to thrive.

버티 그레고리는 대서양의 외딴 섬, 아조레스로 향합니다. 유럽 최대 규모의 해양 보호구역으로 둘러싸인 이 해역은 풍부한 먹이 공급지에 이끌려 이동하는 포식자들에게 중요한 기항지입니다. 버티에게는 보기 드문 자연의 장관을 포착하기에 완벽한 시기입니다. 포식자들이 모여 베이트볼이라 불리는 빽빽한 물고기 떼를 사냥하는 순간이죠. 하지만 예측 불가능한 폭풍 때문에 촬영은 쉽지 않을 것입니다. 버티는 여행 중에 이 지역의 어두운 해양 착취 역사도 탐구합니다. 전직 포경업자에서 고래 관찰자로 변신한 한 남자를 만나, 포경의 종식이 어떻게 아조레스를 보호구역으로 변모시켰는지, 그리고 그 결과 해양 생물이 다시 살아나고 섬세한 먹이 사슬이 번성하게 되었는지 알게 됩니다.

it.title: Delfini da vicino con Bertie Gregory | Trailer ufficiale | National Geographic
it.description:
Bertie Gregory si dirige alle Azzorre, un remoto arcipelago nell'Oceano Atlantico. Circondate dalla più grande area marina protetta d'Europa, queste acque rappresentano una tappa fondamentale per i predatori migratori, attratti dalle ricche zone di alimentazione. È il momento perfetto per Bertie per immortalare un raro spettacolo naturale: quando predatori sfuggenti si uniscono per cacciare densi banchi di pesci chiamati "bait balls". Ma con tempeste imprevedibili, le riprese non saranno facili. Durante il suo viaggio, Bertie esplora anche la cupa storia di sfruttamento marino della regione. Incontrando un ex baleniere diventato osservatore di balene, scopre come la fine della caccia alle balene abbia trasformato le Azzorre in un santuario, consentendo alla vita marina di tornare e alle delicate catene alimentari di prosperare.

de-DE.title: Delfine hautnah mit Bertie Gregory | Offizieller Trailer | National Geographic
de-DE.description:
Bertie Gregory macht sich auf den Weg zu den Azoren, einer abgelegenen Inselkette im Atlantik. Umgeben von Europas größtem Meeresschutzgebiet sind diese Gewässer ein wichtiger Rastplatz für wandernde Raubtiere, die von den reichen Nahrungsgründen hierhergezogen werden. Für Bertie ist es der perfekte Zeitpunkt, ein seltenes Naturschauspiel einzufangen – wenn sich scheue Raubtiere zusammentun, um dichte Fischschwärme, sogenannte Köderbälle, zu jagen. Doch aufgrund unberechenbarer Stürme werden die Dreharbeiten nicht einfach. Auf seiner Reise erkundet Bertie auch die dunkle Geschichte der Meeresausbeutung in der Region. Durch die Begegnung mit einem ehemaligen Walfänger, der zum Walbeobachter wurde, erfährt er, wie das Ende des Walfangs die Azoren in ein Schutzgebiet verwandelte, das die Rückkehr des Meereslebens und das Gedeihen empfindlicher Nahrungsketten ermöglichte.

pl.title: Delfiny z bliska z Bertiem Gregorym | Oficjalny zwiastun | National Geographic
pl.description:
Bertie Gregory udaje się na Azory, odległy łańcuch wysp na Oceanie Atlantyckim. Otoczone największym w Europie morskim obszarem chronionym, wody te stanowią ważny przystanek dla migrujących drapieżników, przyciąganych tu bogatymi żerowiskami. To idealny moment dla Bertiego, aby uchwycić rzadki spektakl natury – kiedy nieuchwytne drapieżniki łączą się, by polować na gęste ławice ryb zwane kulami przynęty. Jednak nieprzewidywalne sztormy utrudniają filmowanie. Podczas swojej podróży Bertie zgłębia również mroczną historię eksploatacji mórz w tym regionie. Spotykając byłego wielorybnika, który został obserwatorem wielorybów, odkrywa, jak koniec wielorybnictwa przekształcił Azory w sanktuarium, umożliwiając powrót życia morskiego i rozwój delikatnych łańcuchów pokarmowych.

ja.title: バーティ・グレゴリーとイルカを間近に観察 | 公式予告編 | ナショナルジオグラフィック
ja.description:
バーティー・グレゴリーは、大西洋に浮かぶ孤島、アゾレス諸島へと向かう。ヨーロッパ最大の海洋保護区に囲まれたこの海域は、豊かな餌場を求めて集まる回遊性捕食動物にとって重要な中継地点となっている。バーティーにとって、希少な自然現象を捉えるには絶好の時期だ。それは、捕獲困難な捕食動物たちが集結し、ベイトボールと呼ばれる密集した魚群を捕食する光景だ。しかし、予測不能な嵐のため、撮影は容易ではない。旅の途中、バーティーはこの地域の海洋搾取の暗い歴史にも迫る。元捕鯨船員で現在はクジラ観察者を務める人物と出会い、捕鯨の終焉がアゾレス諸島を聖域へと変貌させ、海洋生物の復活と繊細な食物連鎖の繁栄を可能にした経緯を紐解く。

fr-FR.title: Les dauphins au plus près avec Bertie Gregory | Bande-annonce officielle | National Geographic
fr-FR.description:
Bertie Gregory se rend aux Açores, un archipel isolé de l'océan Atlantique. Entourées de la plus grande aire marine protégée d'Europe, ces eaux constituent une étape essentielle pour les prédateurs migrateurs, attirés par leurs riches zones d'alimentation. C'est le moment idéal pour Bertie d'immortaliser un spectacle naturel rare : des prédateurs insaisissables se rassemblent pour chasser d'épais bancs de poissons, appelés « ballons d'appâts ». Mais avec des tempêtes imprévisibles, filmer ne sera pas chose aisée. Au cours de son voyage, Bertie explore également la sombre histoire de l'exploitation marine de la région. En rencontrant un ancien baleinier devenu observateur de baleines, il découvre comment la fin de la chasse à la baleine a transformé les Açores en sanctuaire, permettant le retour de la vie marine et le maintien de chaînes alimentaires fragiles. Explorez le monde avec les abonnements National Geographic : http://natgeo.com/ytngmagazine

id.title: Lumba-lumba dari Dekat bersama Bertie Gregory | Trailer Resmi | National Geographic
id.description:
Bertie Gregory menuju Azores, gugusan pulau terpencil di Samudra Atlantik. Dikelilingi oleh kawasan lindung laut terbesar di Eropa, perairan ini merupakan persinggahan penting bagi predator yang bermigrasi, yang tertarik ke sini oleh tempat makan yang kaya. Inilah saat yang tepat bagi Bertie untuk mengabadikan pemandangan alam yang langka—ketika predator yang sulit ditangkap bersatu untuk memburu gerombolan ikan padat yang disebut bola umpan. Namun, dengan badai yang tak terduga, pengambilan gambar menjadi tidak mudah. Selama perjalanannya, Bertie juga menjelajahi sejarah kelam eksploitasi laut di wilayah tersebut. Dengan bertemu seorang mantan pemburu paus yang kini menjadi pengamat paus, ia menemukan bagaimana berakhirnya perburuan paus mengubah Azores menjadi suaka margasatwa, yang memungkinkan kehidupan laut pulih dan rantai makanan yang rapuh berkembang.

nl-NL.title: Dolfijnen van dichtbij met Bertie Gregory | Officiële trailer | National Geographic
nl-NL.description:
Bertie Gregory reist af naar de Azoren, een afgelegen eilandengroep in de Atlantische Oceaan. Omringd door Europa's grootste beschermde zeegebied, vormen deze wateren een onmisbare halteplaats voor migrerende roofdieren, die hierheen worden gelokt door rijke voedselgebieden. Het is het perfecte moment voor Bertie om een zeldzaam natuurspektakel vast te leggen: wanneer ongrijpbare roofdieren zich verenigen om te jagen op dichte scholen vis, zogenaamde aasballen. Maar met onvoorspelbare stormen zal filmen niet eenvoudig zijn. Tijdens zijn reis verkent Bertie ook de duistere geschiedenis van mariene exploitatie in de regio. Door een ontmoeting met een voormalig walvisvaarder die walvisspotter werd, ontdekt hij hoe het einde van de walvisvaart de Azoren heeft veranderd in een toevluchtsoord, waardoor het zeeleven kon terugkeren en kwetsbare voedselketens konden floreren.

pt-BR.title: Golfinhos de Perto com Bertie Gregory | Trailer Oficial | National Geographic
pt-BR.description:
Bertie Gregory ruma aos Açores, um arquipélago remoto no Oceano Atlântico. Rodeadas pela maior área marinha protegida da Europa, estas águas são uma paragem vital para predadores migratórios, atraídos para cá pelas suas ricas áreas de alimentação. É o momento perfeito para Bertie captar um raro espetáculo natural: quando predadores esquivos se unem para caçar cardumes densos de peixes chamados bolas de isca. Mas, com tempestades imprevisíveis, filmar não será fácil. Durante a sua viagem, Bertie também explora a história obscura da exploração marinha na região. Ao conhecer um ex-baleeiro que se tornou observador de baleias, descobre como o fim da caça às baleias transformou os Açores num santuário, permitindo o regresso da vida marinha e o desenvolvimento de delicadas cadeias alimentares.

hi.title: डॉल्फ़िन्स अप क्लोज़ विद बर्टी ग्रेगरी | आधिकारिक ट्रेलर | नेशनल ज्योग्राफ़िक
hi.description:
बर्टी ग्रेगरी अटलांटिक महासागर में एक सुदूर द्वीप श्रृंखला, अज़ोरेस की ओर जा रहे हैं। यूरोप के सबसे बड़े समुद्री संरक्षित क्षेत्र से घिरे ये जलक्षेत्र, प्रवासी शिकारियों के लिए एक महत्वपूर्ण पड़ाव हैं, जो समृद्ध चारागाहों द्वारा यहाँ खींचे चले आते हैं। बर्टी के लिए यह एक दुर्लभ प्राकृतिक दृश्य को कैद करने का एकदम सही समय है—जब मायावी शिकारी, बैट बॉल्स नामक मछलियों के घने झुंडों का शिकार करने के लिए एकजुट होते हैं। लेकिन अप्रत्याशित तूफ़ानों के साथ, फिल्मांकन आसान नहीं होगा। अपनी यात्रा के दौरान, बर्टी इस क्षेत्र के समुद्री शोषण के काले इतिहास की भी पड़ताल करते हैं। एक पूर्व व्हेल शिकारी से मिलकर, जो अब व्हेल खोजकर्ता बन गया है, वह यह पता लगाता है कि कैसे व्हेलिंग के अंत ने अज़ोरेस को एक अभयारण्य में बदल दिया, जिससे समुद्री जीवन की वापसी हुई और नाजुक खाद्य श्रृंखलाएँ फल-फूल सकीं।

es-US.title: Delfines de cerca con Bertie Gregory | Tráiler oficial | National Geographic
es-US.description:
Bertie Gregory se dirige a las Azores, una remota cadena de islas en el océano Atlántico. Rodeadas por la mayor área marina protegida de Europa, estas aguas son una parada vital para los depredadores migratorios, atraídos por sus ricas zonas de alimentación. Es el momento perfecto para que Bertie capture un espectáculo natural excepcional: cuando los escurridizos depredadores se unen para cazar densos bancos de peces llamados bolas de cebo. Pero con tormentas impredecibles, filmar no será fácil. Durante su viaje, Bertie también explora la oscura historia de explotación marina de la región. Al conocer a un exballenero convertido en avistador de ballenas, descubre cómo el fin de la caza de ballenas transformó las Azores en un santuario, permitiendo el regreso de la vida marina y el desarrollo de las delicadas cadenas alimentarias. Explora el mundo con las suscripciones de National Geographic: http://natgeo.com/ytngmagazine

➡ Suscríbete: http://bit.ly/NatGeoSubscribe

National Geographic es el principal destino mundial para la ciencia, la exploración y la aventura. A través de sus científicos, fotógrafos, periodistas y cineastas de talla mundial, National Geographic te acerca a las historias que importan y te lleva más allá de lo posible.

snippet.title: LISA - DREAM feat. Kentaro Sakaguchi (Official Short Film MV)
snippet.description:
LISA’s debut album, ‘Alter Ego’ is out now. Listen here: https://lisa.lnk.to/AlterEgo   
Shop vinyl, CDs, photobooks and more: https://lnk.to/LisaStore 

Follow LISA: 
http://www.instagram.com/lalalalisa_m
https://www.tiktok.com/@lalalalisa_m
https://www.youtube.com/@lalalalisa_m

Follow WeAreLLOUD:
http://www.instagram.com/wearelloud
https://www.tiktok.com/@wearelloud
http://www.facebook.com/wearelloud
https://www.youtube.com/@wearelloud/videos

Lyrics:
I’ve been thinking 
That I got no idea what you’re thinking 
Are you happy? Are you sad?
Are you always gonna hate me for that night in Tokyo? 
When it ended 
I kinda hoped that it’d be open ended
But you never looked back 
Well I guess you can’t hold on to something once you let it go 
But I know a place 
Where we can be us
I know it ain’t real 
But it’s real enough 
From sun going down to sun coming up 
It’s like you’re here with me 
Whenever I close my eyes
It’s taking me back in time
Been drowning in dreams lately 
Like it’s 2019 baby 
Whenever I’m missing you 
Call you up but I can’t get through
Don’t know where you sleep lately 
But I’ll see you in my dreams maybe 
We can catch up, drive down our old street
If all that we were is all that we’ll ever be
It’s bittersweet
At least a girl can dream 
I guess that I’m taking what I can get 
‘Cause I don’t get nothing new from your friends 
If you got the harder side of the break 
Then why is it harder for me to take 
There’s so much I might never get to say, ay
But I know a place 
Where we can be us
I know it ain’t real 
But it’s real enough 
From sun going down to sun coming up 
It’s like you’re here with me 
Whenever I close my eyes
It’s taking me back in time
Been drowning in dreams lately 
Like it’s 2019 baby 
Whenever I’m missing you 
Call you up but I can’t get through
Don’t know where you sleep lately 
But I’ll see you in my dreams maybe 
We can catch up, drive down our old street
If all that we were is all that we’ll ever be
It’s bittersweet
At least a girl can dream 
I-I-I know it’s only in my mind
Playing three nights on the stereo
Like a movie scene, DiCaprio 
Oh l-I-I put my make up on just to fall asleep
It’s like you’re here with me 
Whenever I close my eyes
It’s taking me back in time
Been drowning in dreams lately 
Like it’s 2019 baby 
Whenever I’m missing you 
Call you up but I can’t get through
Don’t know where you sleep lately 
But I’ll see you in my dreams maybe 
We can catch up, drive down our old street
If all that we were is something we’ll never be
It’s bittersweet
Can we be friends at least

snippet.title: Bipul Chettri - Eh Saathi (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
'Eh Saathi' is the first release from the forthcoming album, 'Pravah'. As the title suggests, it's an ode to childhood friendships that transcends time. Almost written like a conversation piece put to music, the song embodies the notion of friendship that is something to nurture and celebrate, that you never take them for granted and its enduring nature of emphasizing loyalty, love, and the shared journey of life.

Please switch on the CC button for English subtitles.

MUSIC
Bipul Chettri - Vocals, Guitars, Backing Vocals 
Pranai Gurung - Guitars
Rahul Rai - Bass
Rythem Bansal - Keys/Organ
Shantanu Sudarshan - Drums/Percussions 
Sumimardor Diengdoh, Bhushan Man Amatya, Prashansa Pandey Amatya - Backing Vocals 

Written and arranged by Bipul Chettri.
Recorded at Baa Baa Black Sheep Studios, Plug ‘N’ Play Studios & Project Studio Productions.
Recording Engineers - Jonty Indra, Anindo Bose, Binaya Man Amatya 
Mixed & Mastered by Binaya Man Amatya
Album Cover Design - Manohar Rai
Album Cover Photography - Praveen Chettri
Producer - Bipul Chettri
Executive Producer - Sonam Tashi 

VIDEO
Directed by Dishant Pradhan
Director of Photography: Vashistha Pradhan 
Chief Assistant Director: Sujan Lamjel
Edited by: Dishant & Vazzu
Art Director: Tejistha Pradhan
Costume Designer: Pfulmaya
Assistant Costume Designer: Subeksha Gurung 
Assistant Cinematographer: Akash Pradhan 
Production House: Lasta Studio 
Assistant Production Manager: Nuhang Subba 
Colorist: Shiny Syko
Lead Cast: Rahul N Mukhia, Kewal Subba, Tenzein Choden, Yowash Lepcha, Adarsh Dewan, Kavya Pradhan.

LYRICS
ए साथी, कस्तो चल्दै छ तेरो जीवन?
मेरो नि ठीकै छ भन्नु, पर्यो यहाँ।
ए साथी, किन लाग्छ सबै नौलो यहाँ?
हामी यस्तै थियौं हैन, एक जमाना।

हुरी बतास संगै उड्ने गर्थ्यौं हामी,
रातभरी जागी, गाउने गर्थ्यौं हामी।
हार केहि संग मान्दैन थियौं हामी,
संसारलाई जिति सके थियौं हामी।
हैन साथी… आः हा…

ए साथी, थाहा छ हामी साना खिरी
तेरो बाको चुरोट चोरी, तान्ने गर्थ्यौं।
एक अर्काको लागि हामी कोही संग, 
लड्नु, मर्नु, जहिले नि रेडी हुन्थ्यौं।

दिनभरीभरी संगै बिताएनि,
रात परेपछि, फेरि भेट्ने गर्थ्यौं।
किन हो किन त्यो पलहरू सोची अझै,
हाँसी पठाउँद छु, सम्झी कुरा धेरै।
ए साथी… आः हा… आः हा…

मलाई चिन्ने अरू कोही
तं जति छैन जस्तो लाग्छ
मेरो कुरा तैंले नै बुझे जस्तो लाग्छ।

कति माया पाएँ, कति धोका खाएँ,
कति छाडि गए, कति टाढा आए।
तर त्यो जिन्दगी फेरि पाउन
म जेनै दिने छु साथि 
म जेनै गरने छु

ए साथी… ए साथी…
ए साथी… ए साथी…

© All Rights Reserved by BIPUL CHETTRI. 2025.

रातभरी जागी, गाउने गर्थ्यौं हामी।
हार केहि संग मान्दैन थियौं हामी,
संसारलाई जिति सके थियौं हामी।
हैन साथी… आः हा…

ए साथी, थाहा छ हामी साना खिरी
तेरो बाको चुरोट चोरी, तान्ने गर्थ्यौं।
एक अर्काको लागि हामी कोही संग, 
लड्नु, मर्नु, जहिले नि रेडी हुन्थ्यौं।

दिनभरीभरी संगै बिताएनि,
रात परेपछि, फेरि भेट्ने गर्थ्यौं।
किन हो किन त्यो पलहरू सोची अझै,
हाँसी पठाउँद छु, सम्झी कुरा धेरै।
ए साथी… आः हा… आः हा…

मलाई चिन्ने अरू कोही
तं जति छैन जस्तो लाग्छ
मेरो कुरा तैंले नै बुझे जस्तो लाग्छ।

कति माया पाएँ, कति धोका खाएँ,
कति छाडि गए, कति टाढा आए।
तर त्यो जिन्दगी फेरि पाउन
म जेनै दिने छु साथि 
म जेनै गरने छु

ए साथी… ए साथी…
ए साथी… ए साथी…

en.title: Bipul Chettri - Eh Saathi (Official Music Video)
en.description:
'Eh Saathi' is the first release from the forthcoming album, 'Pravah'. As the title suggests, it's an ode to childhood friendships that transcends time. Almost written like a conversation piece put to music, the song embodies the notion of friendship that is something to nurture and celebrate, that you never take them for granted and its enduring nature of emphasizing loyalty, love, and the shared journey of life.

Please switch on the CC button for English subtitles.

Bipul Chettri - Vocals, Guitars, Backing Vocals 
Pranai Gurung - Guitars
Rahul Rai - Bass

snippet.title: Primitive War - Official Spot | In Theaters August 21
snippet.description:
This ain’t no walk in the park. Watch the full Primitive War trailer now.

'PRIMITIVE WAR' coming to theatres across the USA and Australia AUGUST 21 2025 proudly presented by Fathom Entertainment and Rialto Distribution. Followed by release worldwide.

From director Luke Sparke comes PRIMITIVE WAR based on the popular novel 'The Primitive War' by Ethan Pettus.
Vietnam. 1968. A recon unit known as Vulture Squad is sent to an isolated jungle valley to uncover the fate of a missing Green Beret platoon. They soon discover they are not alone.
Sparke Films in association with Let it be Entertainment and producers Carly Sparke, Carmel Imrie, Luke Sparke, Geoff Imrie and Alex Becconsall presents PRIMITIVE WAR. An action-packed war film that pits battle hardened soldiers against the greatest predators that ever walked the earth.

USA tickets here:  https://hubs.la/Q03ynb130

Presented by Primitive War

#IGN

snippet.description:
🔥 RUTHLESS INVITATIONAL SHOWDOWN S12 🔥
The ultimate battleground is here! 24 of the best teams from across SEA & CSA are set to clash in an intense showdown of strategy, skill, and survival. 🏆

📅 TOURNAMENT SCHEDULE
👉 Playoffs: August 18 – 22
    •    24 Teams divided into 3 Groups (A, B & C)
    •    Round Robin Format
    •    30 Matches across 5 Days (Each group plays 20 matches)

👉 Grand Finals: August 23 – 26
    •    Top 18 Teams from Playoffs
    •    24 Matches across 4 Days
    •    6 Matches Daily
    •    Smash Rule applied on Day 4
    •    Only 1 Champion will rise 👑

🗺️ Map Rotation (Playoffs):
    •    Matches 1, 3, 5 → ERANGEL
    •    Matches 2, 4, 6 → MIRAMAR

⏰ Match Times (GMT +7):
    •    Match 1 → 17:40
    •    Match 2 → 18:20
    •    Match 3 → 19:00
    •    Match 4 → 19:40
    •    Match 5 → 20:20
    •    Match 6 → 21:00

⚔️ GROUPS LINEUP

GROUP A
🇮🇩 Alter Ego Ares | 🇲🇾 TODAK | 🇹🇭 Vampire Esports | 🇻🇳 Team Secret | 🇳🇵 HORAA Esports | 🇲🇾 Team 52 | 🇮🇩 RRQ RYU | 🇲🇾 Homebois

🇮🇩 BOOM Esports | 🇮🇩 VOIN Esports | 🇲🇾 SEM9 | 🇹🇭 EArena | 🇲🇳 Alpha Gaming | 🇻🇳 MGN Vikings Esports | 🇵🇰 4Thrives Esports | 🇳🇵 Tribe Aeromacy

-------------------------------------------------------------- 
  
Welcome to Day 1 of the 2025 PUBG MOBILE National Championship South Asia Fall Grand Finals.
From 15th to 17th August, the Top 16 teams from the Playoffs will compete in a three-day showdown, playing 5 matches per day starting at 18:00 GMT +5:45.
The finalists will share a $10,000 prize pool, but only the Top 2 teams will secure seeding slots for the 2025 PMSL CSA Fall. One Dream, One Victory.

While the best teams fight in the PMNC Grand Finals, your journey can start now!
Sign up for the PUBG MOBILE Nepal Series (PMNS) S3 and take your first step to the big stage.

April 15th–17th, 2025

snippet.title: Rachana Dahal - Hey Bhagwan (Music Video) ft. Roshan Sharma (Re-mixed and Remastered)
snippet.description:
A heartfelt creation by Mantra Guitar, made possible through the Mantra Artist Fund, in support of independent artists everywhere.
This project holds a special place in my heart. Robin Sharma and I had been wanting to work together for a long time — but the universe had other plans. Instead, it brought together a different constellation of people, energy, and timing… and somehow, this universe happened, HEY BHAGWAN.

I’m deeply grateful to have been involved in this journey and to share it with you Meow.

snippet.title: Mutu Mai Basecha - Female Version (Alternate/Extended) Bashiruddin Miyan
snippet.description:
Mutu Mae Basecha - Female Version (Alternate/Extended) Bashiruddin Miyan

🎶 Mutu Mai Basechha (Female Version Cover) 🎶

Originally performed by Brijesh Shrestha/Samikshya Adhikari, this is my heartfelt female interpretation of the beautiful song Mutu Mai Basechha. I've added some extra verses to express a different emotional perspective—one that reflects a softer, more intimate side of the story.

✨ This version is not just a cover—it's a reimagined expression of love, pain, and longing from a female voice. I hope you connect with this rendition just as deeply as I did while creating it.

🎧 Original Song Credits:
Title: Mutu Mai Basechha
Original Artist: Brijesh Shrestha & Samiksha Adhikari

snippet.description:
Presenting official lyric video of the biggest love song of the year #Pardesiya 
Breathe it. Feel it. Live it! Let love take over your heart! 💞

🎧 Listen Now On:

➟ Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/track/0q84FggW57NXGtLHoetS0Y?si=69de460ee14e4e86

➟ Amazon Music: https://music.amazon.com/tracks/B0FKBYPVWX?marketplaceId=A3K6Y4MI8GDYMT&musicTerritory=IN&ref=dm_sh_itcKlOS1hQjmeCl5whC70Vcmn 

🎬 Create your version of #Pardesiya on:
➟ YouTube Shorts: https://youtube.com/source/kMyTKHEJ-6c/shorts?feature=shared
➟ Instagram Reels: https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/1097832552230653?igsh=MTV5M3pkaHB2MjJmNg

#ParamSundari releasing in cinemas worldwide on 29th August 2025.

🎧 Song Credits :

🎶 Music : Sachin-Jigar 
🎤 Singer : Sonu Nigam  Krishnakali Saha & Sachin-Jigar
➟ Lyrics : Amitabh Bhattacharya 
➟ Programmed & Arranged : Sachin - Jigar
➟ Additional Programming- Sahil Vishwakarma (White Noise Collectives) 
➟ Music Production Head : Romil Ved
➟ Guitars : Sahil Vishwakarma
➟ Flutes : Naveen Kumar 
➟ Backing Vocals - Anandi-Aheeri, Sahil
➟ Recording Engineer : Swar Mehta (White Noise Collectives)
➟ Mixed & Mastered : Eric Pillai @ FSOB
➟ Assistant mix Engineer - Michael Edwin Pillai

🎬 Video Credits

Maddock Films presents #ParamSundari In cinemas on 29th August 2025

➟ Cast: Sidharth Malhotra and Janhvi Kapoor 
➟ Produced By: Dinesh Vijan
➟ Directed By: Tushar Jalota
➟ Co-Producers: Sharada Karki Jalota & Poonam Shivdasani
➟ Director Of Photography : Santhanakrishnan
➟ Story by: Gaurav Mishra, Aarsh Vora, Tushar Jalota
➟ Screenplay and Dialogues: Aarsh Vora, Tushar Jalota
➟ Music By: Sachin-Jigar
➟ Background Score: Sachin-Jigar
➟ Lyrics: Amitabh Bhattacharya 
➟ Additional Dialogues: Gaurav Mishra
➟ Costume Designer : Sheetal Iqbal Sharma
➟ Director Of Choreography: Brinda Gopal
➟ Publicity Design: Himanshu & Rahul Nanda (H-One)
➟ Lyric Video: Latikesh Sutar

Lyrics:

Pardesiya..
Hai tere pyar mein jab se
Jhankaar si..
Hai dil ke taar mein tab se

Tum ho mere jaanta hun magar
Pohchaauñ tum tak ye kaise khabar

Kab se hun main ummeed meiñ
Hai ankaha jo sun lo agar

Pardesiya..
Mila hai tu mujhe jab se

Maiñ qaid huñ
Tere bhi pyar mein tab se ..

Pardesiya haiñ teri batiyoñ ne 
Kiya pareshan pardesiya..

Pardesiya haiñ teri ankhiyoñ ke
Dil pe nishaan pardesiya..
 
Chhoo ke laboñ se jaise
Jaadu hi kar diya
Saavan ne morni ko
Qaabu mein kar liya

Hum dono ki juda theeñ hastiyaañ
Hoñ kinara bin jaise kashtiyaañ

Aasaan ho aage safar
Tum saath mera chun lo agar

Pardesiya.. 

#SonuNigam #SidharthMalhotra #JanhviKapoor

snippet.title: Minecraft Speedrunning (I'M LIVE AGAIN)
snippet.description:
Minecraft Speedrunning (I'M LIVE AGAIN)

DISCLAIMER: I am CHEATING! (Technically)

I am using mods that are not allowed in official leaderboard speedruns. This is practice for my videos, not for world records! I am also simulating ender eye calculation using a mod, I am only throwing the eyes to simulate a time spend, as official speedrunners use a bot to calculate the stronghold location off of 1/2 ender eyes.

I am also using no fog, optifine zoom, increased pearl rates (matching 1.16 rates), and a custom f3 menu with Nether Coordinates. (And maybe more, idk, who cares)

Your love feels like a Sunday
When you got nowhere to go
Oh I love
Your love your love
Your la la la la love
(Your love your love your love)

snippet.title: SHANKARA (Official Video)I Power Star Pawan Singh I Kingstuff IGanesh Acharya I Ullumanati I Mahadev
snippet.description:
SHANKARA (Official Video) I Pawan Singh I Kingstuff I Ganesh Acharya I Ullumanati IMahadev Song 2025 #pawansingh #mahadev #pawansinghnewsong #shiv 

 
🔥 “Shankara” The New Age Mahadev Anthem is here! Experience the power, devotion, and energy like never before with Power Star Pawan Singh in this electrifying musical journey, directed and choreographed by Bollywood legend Ganesh Acharya.
 
OUT NOW – Witness the magic before the full release!

👉 Don’t forget to LIKE, COMMENT, SHARE & SUBSCRIBE for more Mahadev songs, Bhojpuri hits, and power-packed performances by Pawan Singh.
 
⸻
 
🎵 Song Credits
 
Audio

🎤 Singer : Power Star Pawan Singh
🎤 Rap: Kingstuff
🎼 Music & Lyrics: Ullumanati
🎼 Mix Master : Amit Monga

 
Video
Cast: Power Star Pawan Singh
Director & Choreographer: Ganesh Acharya
DOP: Ajay Pandey
Editor: Manoj Magar
Online Editor : Sayan Mal
Colorist : R P Singh
VFX : 4K Visuals 
Costumes : Jayshree 
Line Production : Monty Productions 
 
⸻
 
Produced by: Rashmi Devi Films Productions Pvt. Ltd.
Digital Partner: Global Music Junction Pvt. Ltd.
Promotions: RD Music & Records Team
Poster Design: Aman Kalsi
 
⸻

Lyrics : 

Bina tere ye kut halahal
Kaun hai peene wala re
Kal kut ka kare varan wo
Kaun hai jeene wala re
Bhal chandra bole bhandari 
Aan padi hai vipda bhari
Kasht niware kaun humaro
Surpati aye sharan tihari

Kal garal ye kanth ramaye vastu digambara shankara


Shankara Shankara
Vishambhara 
Shankara


bethe dhyaan magan bje dadum dum dum damru tera
bethe atal atari bhole ka kailash pe dera
vipda padi asur Gano pe sbne tera naam pukara
bachalo mahade sb dekhen ab rasta tera
pee gye bhole vish ka payala 
dhehke ab kanth mein jawala
gal neela padne lga toh
Gora maiyan ne smbhala
bethe fr dhyaan m bhole
har koi har har bole
gunje fr naam tera jai jai ho
vishambhraaaaaaa


Tere gale mai jo mala bhujango ki
Saje hai kanth mai visdhar bada
(Tere gale mai samaya jo pyala ye
Jawala ka na se bhayankar sada) x2

(Bane sanghni aadi teri 
Anhad naad samadi teri
Teen bhuwan mai kaun hai duja 
Kate hai jissay vyadi meri) x2

Bhujunga bhusan dhyan dharo re ab to maheswara


shankara Shankara
Visambhara
shankara

 
📌 Follow RD Music & Records on Instagram
 

https://www.instagram.com/rd_musicindia

snippet.title: अच्युतम केशवम - Lyrical | Achyutam Keshavam Krishna Damodaram | Krishna Bhajan | Janmashtami 2025
snippet.description:
✨ अच्युतम केशवम् – श्रीकृष्ण भक्ति गीत ✨
 "अच्युतम केशवम्" एक अनुपम और मन को शांति देने वाला भजन है, जो भगवान श्रीकृष्ण और भगवान विष्णु की महिमा का गुणगान करता है। इसमें प्रभु के अनेक नाम प्रेमपूर्वक उच्चारित किए जाते हैं, जिनमें गहन आध्यात्मिक अर्थ निहित है।
यह भजन गाने से हृदय पवित्र होता है, दुख दूर होते हैं और परमात्मा की कृपा प्राप्त होती है। यह हमें पूर्ण समर्पण का मार्ग सिखाता है और याद दिलाता है कि भगवान सदैव हमारे रक्षक हैं।

✨ Achyutam Keshavam – A Devotional Krishna Bhajan ✨
 "Achyutam Keshavam" is a timeless and soul-soothing bhajan dedicated to Lord Krishna, praising their divine names, virtues, and forms. The bhajan beautifully recites various names of the Lord - Achyuta, Keshava, Narayana, and more - each carrying deep spiritual meaning.
Singing this bhajan is believed to purify the heart, remove sorrows, and bring the blessings of the Supreme Lord. It reminds devotees to surrender completely to God, trusting His eternal protection and grace.


🌸 Chant “Achyutam Keshavam” with devotion and invite divine bliss into your life.

Credits:
Singer - Saee Tembhekar
Music - Kamlesh Bhadkamkar
Lyrics - Traditional
Chorus - Shripad Lele, Vivek Naik, Unmesh Chandavarkar, Shardul Kavthekar, Seema Lele, Mrunmayi Dadke, Sapna Heman, Dhanashree Kashid
Flute - Varad Kathapurkar
Rhythm - Archis Lele, Hanumant Rawade, Vijay Jadhav, Anil Karanjavkar, Shashank Hadkar, Bharat Bhadkamkar
Guitar - Rahul Deo
Sound Engineer - Shrikrishna Sawant

To receive regular updates on devotional songs subscribe to us on the following link: https://www.youtube.com/BhaktiPrem

Lyrics:

अच्युतम केशवं कृष्ण दामोदरं,
राम नारायणं जानकी वल्लभम ।

कौन कहते हे भगवान आते नहीं,
तुम मीरा के जैसे बुलाते नहीं ।

कौन कहते है भगवान खाते नहीं,
बेर शबरी के जैसे खिलाते नहीं ।

कौन कहते है भगवान सोते नहीं,
माँ यशोदा के जैसे सुलाते नहीं ।

कौन कहते है भगवान नाचते नहीं,
गोपियों की तरह तुम नचाते नहीं ।

नाम जपते चलो काम करते चलो,
हर समय कृष्ण का ध्यान करते चलो ।

याद आएगी उनको कभी ना कभी,
कृष्ण दर्शन तो देंगे कभी ना कभी ।

Achyutam Keshavam Krishna Damodaram
 Ram Narayanam Janaki Vallabham

Kaun Kehte Hain Bhagwan Aate Nahin
 Tum Meera Ke Jaise Bulaate Nahin

Kaun Kehte Hain Bhagwan Khaate Nahin
 Ber Shabari Ke Jaise Khilaate Nahin
 
Kaun Kehte Hain Bhagwan Sote Nahin
 Maa Yashoda Ke Jaise Sulaate Nahin

Kaun Kehte Hain Bhagwan Naachte Nahin
 Gopiyon Ki Tarah Tum Nachaate Nahin

Naam Japte Chalo Kaam Karte Chalo
 Har Samay Krishna Ka Dhyaan Karte Chalo

Yaad Aayegi Unko Kabhi Na Kabhi
 Krishna Darshan To Denge Kabhi Na Kabhi

अच्युतम केशवम - Lyrical | Achyutam Keshavam Krishna Damodaram | Krishna Bhajan

hi.title: फ्रेंकलिन मोटू पतलू सिटी फुरफरी नगर में नया घर भारतीय बाइक ड्राइविंग 3 डी में
hi.description:
इंडियन बाइक्स ड्राइविंग 3D में मोटू पतलू के फुरफुरी नगर में फ्रैंकलिन का नया घर | गेमप्ले #17

इस वीडियो में फ्रैंकलिन अपने नए घर को मोटू पतलू के फुरफुरी नगर गाँव में स्थानांतरित करते हैं, जहाँ उन्होंने अपना घर मोटू पतलू के घर के बगल में रखा है। इस वीडियो में फ्रैंकलिन मेयर श्री सिंह, इंस्पेक्टर चिंगम, डॉ. झटका चायवाला और घासीराम से मिलते हैं और फ्रैंकलिन अपने परिवार से भी मिलते हैं। उन्होंने फुरफुरी नगर गाँव की खोज की।

इंस्टाग्राम: https://www.instagram.com/gamesticbro?igsh=amdzZzU5YjdwZ2wx

गेम क्रेडिट; रोहित गेमिंग स्टूडियो

वीडियो में निम्नलिखित विषय शामिल हैं
1. मोटू पतलू भारतीय बाइक ड्राइविंग 3डी में
2. फुरफुरी नगर में फ्रैंकलिन हाउस भारतीय बाइक ड्राइविंग 3डी
3. मोटू पतलू भारतीय बाइक ड्राइविंग 3डी में फ्रैंकलिन
4. मोटू पतलू भारतीय बाइक ड्राइविंग 3डी
5. फ्रैंकलिन अपने परिवार से मिलें भारतीय बाइक ड्राइविंग 3डी

snippet.title: Spending $8,492,739 For The GOLDEN GOOSE In Grow A Garden..
snippet.description:
Today I spent all my robux to get the golden goose in Grow A Garden! Make sure you watch the whole video to find out what happens. 

FOLTYN MERCH: https://foltyn.shop/

--Socials--

Discord: https://discord.gg/hqwZhrkqRr

Roblox Group: https://www.roblox.com/groups/1177555...

Roblox Name: TheRealFoltyn

Insta: https://www.instagram.com/foltynn/

Twitter: https://twitter.com/Foltynnn

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.
